      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold font-heading mt-2 mb-4">Paring Disc Blockage: Causes, Symptoms &amp; How to Clear It</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg max-w-2xl mb-6">Paring disc blockage stops product flow from a disc centrifuge without any obvious mechanical failure. Understanding how the paring disc works is the first step to fast diagnosis and prevention.</p>
